
<purchabr>LVI GROUP</purchabr> {<purchcode>LVI</purchcode>} TO MAKE ACQUISITION
    NEW YORK, April 9 - <purchaser>LVI Group Inc</purchaser> said it has <status>agreed in
principle</status> to purchase all outstanding shares of {<acquired>Spectrum
Holding Corp</acquired>} for a proposed <dlramt>13 mln dlrs</dlramt> in cash.
    <purchabr>LVI</purchabr> said an additional 10 mln dlrs in common stock and
